pLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"symbol"}}}